"{\"uid\": \"scientificamerican.com-article-the-olympics-breaking-fiasco-undermined-serious-hip-hop-artists-and-scholars\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Opinion September 4, 2024 5min read The Olympics Breaking Fiasco Undermined Serious Hip-Hop Artists and Scholars The \\\"Raygun\\\" Olympics fiasco points to how hip-hop scholarship is at risk of being colonized and undermined in academia ByA.D.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics Breaking Fiasco Undermined Serious Hip-Hop Artists\", \"from\": 36, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"Scholars\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"The \\\"Raygun\\\" Olympics fiasco points\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop scholarship\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"academia ByA.D.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carson B-Girl Raygun of Team Australia competes during the B-Girls Round Robin, Group B on day 14 of the Olympic Games Paris 2024 at Place de la Concorde on August 09, 2024, in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Carson\", \"score\": 0.9999994936507764, \"rank\": 5.063495575939091e-07, \"text\": \"Carson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Carson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Carson\"}, {\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.7636173053707073, \"rank\": 0.30955649245600364, \"text\": \"Team Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_2014_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australia competes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_2014_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_2014_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9214476562114726e-13, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998358139004551, \"rank\": 0.00016421306124136403, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9730267035486708, \"rank\": 0.027389074004595282, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the B-Girls Round Robin\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"Group B\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ezra Shaw/Getty Images In August Australia's Rachael Gunn, also known as \\\"Raygun,\\\" delivered an Olympics breaking performance more redolent of mockery than mastery of the competitive formbetter known as breakdancing.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.54751648708993e-14, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource