tition.\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6051, \"end\": 6057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"score\": 0.999999282004213, \"rank\": 6.994105655962283e-07, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RCA_Records\"}, {\"begin\": 6058, \"end\": 6066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Montalvo\", \"score\": 0.9995791633636959, \"rank\": 0.0002620815396097881, \"text\": \"Montalvo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Montalvo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juan_Montalvo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S. Olympic breaker\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6024}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6049}, {\"ngram\": \"the attentionby\", \"from\": 6077, \"to\": 6092}, {\"ngram\": \"any type\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6114}, {\"ngram\": \"publicity\", \"from\": 6118, \"to\": 6127}, {\"ngram\": \"good publicity\", \"from\": 6131, \"to\": 6145}, {\"ngram\": \"a good thing\", \"from\": 6167, \"to\": 6179}, {\"ngram\": \"the viral performance\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6210}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6221}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 6237, \"to\": 6245}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaking competition\", \"from\": 6249, \"to\": 6273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I disagree.\", \"from\": 6275, \"to\": 6286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conversations that should be about Black art and hip-hop culture have been focused on a white Australian woman.\", \"from\": 6287, \"to\": 6398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6381, \"end\": 6391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999532614292327, \"rank\": 4.5985167665137593e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://